author: bago
msg: Change DNSServiceXBillImpl callback to use a callback thread because it wasn't respecting the contract.
The callback of an asynch method should never be called by the original caller thread.
A better solution could be to use a thread pool, but the dnsjnio implementation will take care of this.
The DNSJava based Staged executor is simply a proof of concept.
